{"tid":2172580,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓前官員聲稱金正恩陷昏迷　胞妹開始掌權","createTime":"2020-08-24T17:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T21:01:11.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a064b00711bbe36ee80520978f22192696636c38","tid":2172580,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】北韓領袖金正恩的健康再度引起關注。南韓前官員聲稱金正恩已昏迷，胞妹金與正開始接掌權力。<br />\n<br />\n《南韓先驅報》引述南韓前總統金大中的幕僚張誠珉指，從中國得來的消息，認為金正恩陷入昏迷，但生命未結束，近期金正恩出席活動的相片都是假的，聲稱除非病重或因政變而被取代，否則北韓領導人不會將權力交給任何人。<br />\n<br />\n張誠珉稱，由於北韓不能夠長期維持真空狀態，權力繼承的完整架構亦未形成，所以勞動黨第一副部長金與正才獲得部分權力，並被推到黨內前線。<br />\n<br />\n今年四月時亦曾傳出金正恩病危的消息，南韓國家情報院上周向國會匯報時確認，金正恩向金與正等親信下放部分權力，但南韓認為此舉旨在減輕金正恩的施政壓力，分散責任，並非意味已敲定繼任人選，金正恩仍掌控大權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=402950&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Ea0BPee_v3ZxqXZG92qjnIGwMTh3d13NjmG4LtAi5DMLp5sa-zzM07mY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402950%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Ea0BPee_v3ZxqXZG92qjnIGwMTh3d13NjmG4LtAi5DMLp5sa-zzM07mY&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3SbrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=0729143e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D402950%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Ea0BPee_v3ZxqXZG92qjnIGwMTh3d13NjmG4LtAi5DMLp5sa-zzM07mY&h=47d7b214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=402950&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Ea0BPee_v3ZxqXZG92qjnIGwMTh3d13NjmG4LtAi5DMLp5sa-zzM07mY</a>"},{"pid":"7fba4ce58d24844e54344d8ac254a046bfb35bf7","tid":2172580,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T20:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c2d520763df6c7e7bbea9bda68c55b894a7737","tid":2172580,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"